Legislative Document No. 1895
H.P. 1266 House of Representatives, May 5, 2025
An Act to Require the Removal from a Property Tax Lien the Name
of a Previous Owner Who Paid Prorated Property Taxes
Received by the Clerk of the House on May 1, 2025. Referred to the Committee on
Taxation pursuant to Joint Rule 308.2 and ordered printed pursuant to Joint Rule 401.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
